							<p>The success of the scheme rests on ensuring that all the stakeholders adhere to the highest level of medical ethics. EO-Empanelment shall be performing the following medical audit functions:</p> 
							<ul> 
								<li>Monitoring of quality of medical care.</li> 
								<li>Framing guidelines to prevent moral hazard.</li> 
								<li>Monitoring the trends of utilization of listed therapies across NWHs.</li> 
								<li>Conduct investigation into allegations of treatment lapses.</li> 
								<li>Analyze mortality and morbidity under this scheme and recommend corrective measures</li> 
								<li>Recommend punitive actions against a medical professional or NWH.</li> 
							</ul> 
